  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Direct DNA amplification, viral isolation and specific antibody measurement in saliva from
      children attending nursery in France Sample collection will be done by the pediatrician the
      nurse, or one of the authorized investigators of the study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Salivary collection kit. 3 swab for DNA research, 1 for antibodies research and 1 for virus
      isolation by cell growth.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
